Metadata.Title: Deadly Knowledge
Metadata.Description: Good day agent,As usual agent Smith has gotten himself in a pickle... He is stuck, again... He was captured on Ambrose Island and you will need to set him free as what he knows is vital information and needs to be debriefed at the agency.In addition anyone that has become aware of his identity will have to be taken out.Good luck agent, I shall leave you to prepare...Created by ThatGeekyGuy and Cybie.
